# TOP (Display Linux processes)
 
Load avarage: Over the last 1, 5 and 15 munutes 
 
--> Personal command top 

shift + f 
 
--> Enter or left commits, d or space toggles display
--> s  sets sort
--> q or esc to end!

# HTOP 

l list files of processes 

htop -p PID + l Show files of processes 
 
--> 100 igual a 10 segundos no htop 

--> htop -d 100 (Atualiza a cada 10s)

